    "name": "Words of Yendor",
    "steam_appid": 2156830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/2ed477c4d9b5b0a5c15754fa46eed79e.poster.avif?t=1765744245\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/2ed477c4d9b5b0a5c15754fa46eed79e.webm?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/2ed477c4d9b5b0a5c15754fa46eed79e.mp4?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br>Discover the meaning of the <strong>Word of Yendor</strong> in these procedurally generated adventures, set in a steamgoth world of mystery, magic and steam contraptions. Learn the secrets of the <i>White Steam</i> or the <i>Black Smoke</i> perspectives. Explore settlements, solve word puzzles, and find your way to the local Master Villains usurping crucial elements of the mystery. Use your word-solving skills to navigate dangerous obstacles and gather resources. Engage in turn-based word duels against opponents with a unique tactical combat system.<br><br>Each story ending is tailor-made, offering a personalized experience. How is this possible? By leveraging the world's most powerful content creation system!<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/6585debbc971bc45165fa56413aa4b02.poster.avif?t=1765744245\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/6585debbc971bc45165fa56413aa4b02.webm?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/6585debbc971bc45165fa56413aa4b02.mp4?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/b5e62525670c894db6692376234292c3.avif?t=1765744245\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Create turn-based, procedurally generated adventures<br></li><li>Shape your hero or heroine with highly customizable portraits<br></li><li>Master multiple types of word puzzles and word duels, forged into a coherent game system<br></li><li>Duel opponents that also compose words from the same pool of letters as you<br></li><li>Wield words that can literally hurt or mend<br></li><li>Venture into mini-adventures across space-time and the afterworld<br></li><li>Collect and craft items and upgrades, and optionally steal and trade poignant curios<br></li><li>Experience a dynamic, often dramatic or humorous, yet always meaningful and personal story</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/ac12184d7b05d0ab7c874e60835ec541.poster.avif?t=1765744245\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/ac12184d7b05d0ab7c874e60835ec541.webm?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/ac12184d7b05d0ab7c874e60835ec541.mp4?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/68bf7b5780d0d530fcb28ddc5a0575e5.avif?t=1765744245\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A typical adventure can be completed in 30–90 minutes, depending on the complexity level of your choice. Just like a game of chess, Words of Yendor offers endless replayability, providing unique and thrilling adventures each time you play.<br></li><li>Your progress is automatically saved, allowing you to contemplate the challenges for as long as you like. The game remains unaffected by the passage of real time.<br></li><li>Note that embracing the spirit of roguelikes, this is also a “permadeath” game, so if your hero falls, the game is over. However, if you enter the same <i>adventure seed</i> number, you can replay any adventure as many times as you want.<br></li><li>It's never just one of the “red, green, blue” endings. Each one is personal and unique!</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/1c76cba0edeaf214cc8e60568ea129d8.poster.avif?t=1765744245\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/1c76cba0edeaf214cc8e60568ea129d8.webm?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/1c76cba0edeaf214cc8e60568ea129d8.mp4?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/13dbcf0081c929f9d63ac13ff626b136.avif?t=1765744245\" width=616 height=141 /></span></p>",
